    "At the foot of several first-class ski resorts, the small town of Soldeu is a gateway to all kinds of adventures. Postcard views, views of lush mountains and valleys, surrounded by melting rivers, this place has many natural beauties to offer.",
    "Bridge over the Valira d'Orient river with a nice spot to have a picnic and dip your feet in the water.",
    "A popular hiking route between Soldeu and Canillo, with views of the Les Moles Waterfall and the Ransol water canal. Some wooden bridges and narrow paths to navigate the trail."
